# Web WIZARDD — local development environment
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in the real values.
# The `.env` file MUST NEVER be committed. The .gitignore already excludes it.
#
# In production, these same variables are set in the Netlify dashboard for
# wizardd.allegiantdigital.co under Site settings → Environment variables.

# ─── Required for LLM extraction ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Name suggestion: "web-wizardd-dev"
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-PLACEHOLDER_REPLACE_WITH_REAL_KEY

# ─── Optional: override the default Claude model used for extraction ────────
# Defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6 if not set. Switch to claude-haiku-4-5 to cut
# cost for cheap tasks, or claude-opus-4-7 for higher quality on edge A.R.C.s.
# WIZARDD_LLM_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# ─── Optional: control the LLM fixture cache mode ───────────────────────────
# replay   (default) — use cached LLM responses; fast and free
# record            — call the live API and write/overwrite cache fixtures
# live              — call the live API but do not write fixtures
# fallback          — try replay, fall through to live if no fixture exists
# Most of the time you do not set this — npm scripts set it per command.
# LLM_CACHE_MODE=replay

# ─── Required when implementing Layer 2 (Research) ──────────────────────────
# SERP API for live search-result crawling. Serper.dev recommended for v1.
# SERPER_API_KEY=

# ─── Required when implementing the partner-preview signing ─────────────────
# 32+ character secret used to sign one-time partner preview URLs.
# Generate with: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
# PREVIEW_TOKEN_SECRET=
